{"tid":1883081,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"光復YouTube有幾重要？","createTime":"2020-02-16T16:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T17:46:07.000Z","uid":134337,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9177715790996dd65420d4d1da3a2e79ffd9ecb","tid":1883081,"uid":134337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"YouTube影響力唔洗講 <br />\n加上對家好識用依D招數<br />\n因為肺炎 已經搞到遊行集會大大減少 <br />\n唔少淺黃生活好似回復至抗爭前咁<br />\n但我深信全部手足根本忘記唔到一切<br />\n如果我地依一刻連冷氣軍師都唔做 勢力只會不停下降<br />\n<br />\n今次光復YouTube唔止可以重燃鬥心<br />\n仲正正係個大好機會話比全部人知 我地無放棄無忘記<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對家不停做緊野 唔係禁下制都懶呀？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkCa93X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkCa93X.jpg&h=9a86514d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCA0NQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCA0NQD.jpg&h=e9b8053c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/80697011_163116418390061_6657782019897950208_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ohc=19NyfDEsREEAX_EU7B_&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=49f0bbbbb1200ad7321a14615230713b&amp;oe=5ED03B25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F80697011_163116418390061_6657782019897950208_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ohc%3D19NyfDEsREEAX_EU7B_%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D49f0bbbbb1200ad7321a14615230713b%26oe%3D5ED03B25&h=4f6d352e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85d9155f791f6cb76ed04311a74db6b025f58d28","tid":1883081,"uid":141951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"仲有連登都係"},{"pid":"28286b078d3e6dd3f1413007a6482e9216c09827","tid":1883081,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a965ac0634d3e766df902cd57e686c5a7d780d","tid":1883081,"uid":5103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土Youtube Channel？</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867920\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867920</a>"},{"pid":"ac0b953368e0d87a10030990539f18dc9b17356e","tid":1883081,"uid":134337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"踢走假新聞"},{"pid":"fe2ee82e73b74006dd210cdcc3cb795a4b046bb7","tid":1883081,"uid":74554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"唔該大家真係要返一返黎做下正經野"},{"pid":"84408a128008243d4fccabb5105419c87257e23e","tid":1883081,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3b5afb4b531eaa94e56e8c265669b4c57b30a","tid":1883081,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"唔重要根本"},{"pid":"54592b8bdd55958db8efb653c5450119de3fc221","tid":1883081,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:38